<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<%- include('partials/head',{ title : "Cotizador de cortinas" }) %>

  <body>
    <%- include('partials/header') %>
    

          <main class="container">
            <section class="col-12 mt-5 mx-auto">
              <article class="card shadow">
                <div class="card-body">
                  <form class="row" action="">
                    <div class="col-12 col-md-6 col-lg-4 mb-3">
                      <div class="form-floating ">
                        <select class="form-select" id="system">
                          <option selected hidden>Seleccione...</option>
                          <% systems.forEach(system => { %>
                            <option value="<%= system.id %>"><%= system.name %></option>
                          <% }) %>
                        </select>
                        <label for="system">Sistema</label>
                      </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-12 col-md-6 col-lg-4 mb-3">

                      <div class="form-floating">
                        <select class="form-select" id="system">
                          <option selected hidden>Seleccione...</option>
                          <% cloths.forEach(cloth => { %>
                            <option value="<%= cloth.id %>"><%= cloth.name %></option>
                          <% }) %>
                        </select>
                        <label for="system">Tela</label>
                      </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-12 col-md-6 col-lg-4 mb-3">

                      <div class="form-floating">
                        <select class="form-select" id="system">
                          <option selected hidden>Seleccione...</option>
                          <% colors.forEach(color => { %>
                            <option value="<%= color.id %>"><%= color.name %></option>
                          <% }) %>
                        </select>
                        <label for="system">Color</label>
                      </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="col-12 col-md-6 col-lg-4 mb-3">

                      <div class="form-floating ">
                        <select class="form-select" id="system">
                          <option selected hidden>Seleccione...</option>
                          <% supports.forEach(support => { %>
                            <option value="<%= support.id %>"><%= support.name %></option>
                          <% }) %>
                        </select>
                        <label for="system">Soporte</label>
                      </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-12 col-md-6 col-lg-4 mb-3">

                      <div class="form-floating ">
                        <select class="form-select" id="system">
                          <option selected hidden>Seleccione...</option>
                          <% patterns.forEach(pattern => { %>
                            <option value="<%= pattern.id %>"><%= pattern.name %></option>
                          <% }) %>
                        </select>
                        <label for="system">Modelo</label>
                      </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="col-12 col-md-6 col-lg-4 mb-3">

                      <div class="form-floating ">
                        <select class="form-select" id="system">
                          <option selected hidden>Seleccione...</option>
                          <option value="1">One</option>
                          <option value="2">Two</option>
                          <option value="3">Three</option>
                        </select>
                        <label for="system">Cadena</label>
                      </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-12 col-md-6 col-lg-4 mb-3">
                      <div class="form-floating mb-3">
                        <input type="text" class="form-control" id="width">
                        <label for="width">Ancho de pa√±o (cm)</label>
                      </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-12 col-md-6 col-lg-4 mb-3">
                      <div class="form-floating mb-3">
                        <input type="text" class="form-control" id="heigth">
                        <label for="heigth">Alto (cm)</label>
                      </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-12 col-md-6 col-lg-4 mb-3">
                      <div class="form-floating mb-3">
                        <input type="text" class="form-control" id="heigth">
                        <label for="heigth">Nombre de referencia</label>
                      </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-12 col-md-4 mb-3">
                      <div class="alert alert-warning">
                          Todos los campos son obligatorios. Puede ver mas abajo aclaraciones de cada sistema seleccionado.
                      </div>
                  </div>
                  <div class="col-12 col-md-8 mb-3 ">
                      <div class="alert alert-success text-center py-2">
                       <h4>Monto: <span></span></h4>
                      </div>
                      <button class="btn buttons__btn-custom w-100">COTIZAR CORTINA</button>
                  </div>
                    <div class="col-12 mb-3">
                        <div class="alert alert-info">
                          <h6><i class="fas fa-info-circle"></i> Aclaraciones</h6>
                          <hr>
                          <ul>
                            <li>Lo primero que debe seleccionarse es el sistema a cotizar. Ej: <b>Roller</b></li>
                            <li>Las medidas deben ser expresadas en centimetros. Ej: <b>2m = 200cm</b> </li>
                            <li>Consulten con nosotros si el cotizador no cotiza alguna medida.</li>
                          </ul>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                  </form>
                </div>

              </article>

            </section>


          </main>
          <%- include('partials/footer') %>
          <%- include('partials/scripts') %>
  </body>

</html>